SubjectBy-elections (4) - Battlefords–Lloydminster - South Surrey–White Rock - Bonavista–Burin–Trinity - Scarborough–Agincourt
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of Battlefords–Lloydminster - South Surrey–White Rock - Bonavista–Burin–Trinity - Scarborough–Agincourt, with polling to take place on December 11, 2017.
